        public MaxLatestAggregator(Aggregators.Interpolation method,
                           String name,
                           int total_series,
                           long start,
                           long end)
        An aggregator that keeps track of the maximum latest value for each series
        参数:
        method - The interpolation method (not used)
        name - The name of the aggregator
        total_series - The total number of series in the result set, including sub queries and group bys
        start - Query start time in milliseconds for filtering
        end - Query end time in milliseconds for filtering
